    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（一時は元気がなくなってたけど……）\n（最近はみんな順調に練習を頑張ってるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They were a bit down for a while‚ but…)\n(Lately everyone’s been working hard at practice.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、そろそろ休憩を入れてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ maybe it’s time for a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふう、そうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh‚ you’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、かなり踊りましたわね……\nクタクタですわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff… Huff… We danced a lot…\nI’m exhausted~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0612663832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "って言ったのは……誰だっけ？\nあら？　私にかわってセンターになる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who was it that said that again?\nOh? The one who’s going to be center instead of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "うっ。ク、クタクタというのは……\nそう、冗談です！　私はまだまだ平気ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh. E-Exhausted means…\nRight‚ I was joking! I’m still fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、またダンスのキレが戻ってきた気がする！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ I feel like your dancing’s got its sharpness back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なのかな？\n……良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is… that so?\n…That’s good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、サビ直前のターンで\n毎回ちょっとだけ遅れてるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ on the turn right before the chorus‚\nyou might be a little late every time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかもしれませんわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That might be true…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、そういえば\n他の曲でも似た動きで苦戦してなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ now that you mention it‚\nweren’t you struggling with a similar move in another song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "体を使う範囲が大きい動きですから\n柔軟をしっかりやるといいかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a move that uses a wide range of your body‚ so\nit might be good to do some stretching properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私はすずのターンの癖、気付かなかったな……\n渚、凄いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t notice Suzu’s turning habit…\nNagisa‚ you’re amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……ありがとう\n最近、頑張って周りをよく見るようにしてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… Thanks.\nRecently‚ I’ve been trying hard to pay attention to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "さあさあ、すずにゃん。楽しい柔軟の時間だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright alright‚ Suzu-nyan. It’s fun stretching time~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.333333299998,
          "startTime": 86.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 83.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。ちょ、なんで走って追って来るんですの～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? W-Why are you running after me~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 91
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 92.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……{user}さん！\n助けてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant… Pant… {user}-san!\nHelp me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 93.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい……俺を盾にしないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey hey… Don’t use me as a shield.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーとは、身をていしてアイドルを\n守るものでしょう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t a manager supposed to throw themselves in the line of fire\nto protect their idols!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは俺が言うことであって\nアイドル自身が言うことじゃないと思うぞ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that’s something I should be saying‚\nnot something the idol themselves should be saying…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……すずにゃん、早く観念しないと\nもっと大変な目にあっちゃうよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu… Suzu-nyan‚ if you don’t give up soon‚\nyou’ll be in for a much tougher time~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 110.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですの、大変な目って……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-What do you mean‚ a tougher time…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "んー、なんとなく言ってみただけ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I just said it out of the blue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "もう、驚かせないでくださいまし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ don’t scare me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、すずちゃんは体が硬いのに\nいつも柔軟をサボりがちですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Suzu-chan‚ even though you’re not flexible‚\nyou always tend to skip stretching‚ don’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "うっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 139.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣みたいに体をぐにゃぐにゃ～にしとかないとさ\nケガしやすくなっちゃうんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re not all wobbly~ like Mei‚\nwon’t you get hurt more easily?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは確かに、一理ありますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ you do have a point there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "最近はポテトチップスを食べ過ぎているようでしたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you’ve been eating too many potato chips lately‚ so",
